description: Lobster ME prepares all of its lobster with their secret, signature take on the traditional New England fashion. Their signature Lobster Rolls are joined by a selection of all things lobster, including Lobster Mac & Cheese, Lobster Salad, Lobsticle (Fried Lobster Tail on a Stick) and amazing Lobster Ice Cream. If you're hungry just hearing about this, stop by today, and try a bite!
name: LobsterME
